header.title: LLB(Hons) Program Requirements
header.summaryDescription:
Complete 64 units comprising:

  • 36 units for all LLB(Hons) Core Courses, and
  • 8 to 16 units from General Elective Courses, and
  • 12 to 20 units from LLB(Hons) Flexible Core Courses

payload.value:
1. Class of honours

Specific requirements apply to the awarding of honours in this program:

  1. The class of honours is calculated on the basis of the grade point average of the grades obtained by you in the first attempt at all LAWS courses at level 2 or higher that contribute to the program.
  2. Refer to the Bachelor Honours Degree Procedure for more information.
